content:
Validates Svelte component syntax and compiles components to check for errors. Ensures components are production-ready and follows Svelte best practices.

```json
{
  "PostToolUse": [
    {
      "matcher": "Edit|Write",
      "hooks": [
        {
          "type": "command",
          "command": "if [[ \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" == *.svelte ]]; then echo 'üî• Compiling Svelte component...' && npx svelte-check --output human \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" && echo '‚úÖ Svelte component valid' || echo '‚ö†Ô∏è Svelte compilation issues detected'; fi"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```
